<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٢٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٥٣٧٩ -<span class="c5"> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا الثَّوْرِيُّ، عَنْ يُونُسَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ يَكْرَهُ شَهَادَةَ الْأَعْمَى»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>